{"_id":"BtwJVnfkC9twrvmu","name":"Como Jogar","permission":{"default":2,"8m8ua3an3okqKvoB":3},"folder":"lVwMcu6yQZ0LZEhQ","sort":1100000,"flags":{},"content":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Agenda</h2>\n<p>&bull; Play a compromised, active character</p>\n<p>&bull; Imagine dangerous and exciting worlds</p>\n<p>&bull; Play to find out what happens</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Principles</h2>\n<p>&bull; Take risks and embrace the consequences</p>\n<p>&bull; Learn your Archetype&rsquo;s Moves</p>\n<p>&bull; Keep track of your Hooks and say when they apply</p>\n<p>&bull; Step up when it&rsquo;s your turn to shine</p>\n<p>&bull; Step back when it&rsquo;s another player&rsquo;s turn to shine</p>\n<p>&bull; Look after your fellow players</p>\n<p>&bull; Think cinematically</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Always Say</h2>\n<p>&bull; What the Principles demand</p>\n<p>&bull; What honesty demands</p>\n<p>&bull; What the rules demand</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"}
{"_id":"CWragrdQa8rsEWoy","name":"Vehicle Equipment Tags","permission":{"default":2,"8m8ua3an3okqKvoB":3},"folder":"lVwMcu6yQZ0LZEhQ","sort":400000,"flags":{},"content":"<h2>Vehicle Equipment Tags:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Area: It hits everything within Crash range of its target.</li>\n<li>Crash: The crunch and smash of vehicles crashing into each other.</li>\n<li>Dogfighting: Maneuvering and dogfighting, jostling for the perfect shot.</li>\n<li>Discharge: If it&rsquo;s a Move, it&rsquo;s Discharged when it&rsquo;s used. If it&rsquo;s a weapon, Gear, vehicle equipment, or ship module, it&rsquo;s Discharged when a Move says. If it&rsquo;s Shields, it&rsquo;s Discharged when it absorbs Harm.</li>\n<li>Explosive: It explodes, destroying individuals and structures within its blast radius.</li>\n<li>Guided: You have Advantage when firing at a ship or vehicle.</li>\n<li>Hold Off: They&rsquo;re circling from far off, keeping their enemies at bay.</li>\n<li>N Ammo: It can be fired N times before you run out of ammo for it.</li>\n<li>N Damage: It does N Damage to ships and vehicles when it hits.</li>\n</ul>"}
{"_id":"ETKut7EEc8Mawizc","name":"Hesper","permission":{"default":0,"8m8ua3an3okqKvoB":3},"folder":"WJjQBMC4cV0nza4T","sort":800001,"flags":{},"content":"<p>d20 Mutation Effect</p>\n<p>1 <strong>Additional eyes</strong> Target gains light blindness and a +4 bonus to sight-based Perception checks</p>\n<p>2&ndash;3 <strong>Autonomous parasite </strong>Target takes 1d6 slashing damage as a parasite emerges</p>\n<p>4&ndash;5 <strong>Bioelectric cells </strong>Technological items held by the target gain the broken condition for as long as the target holds them</p>\n<p>6&ndash;7 <strong>Claws, spines </strong>Target gains a natural melee attack that deals 1d3+Str piercing damage for Medium or teeth on one limb creatures, but the target also takes a &ndash;2 penalty to attacks with two-handed weapons</p>\n<p>8&ndash;9 <strong>Glowing tumors </strong>Target sheds light as a lantern and takes &ndash;5 penalty to Stealth checks</p>\n<p>10 <strong>Gills </strong>Target gains the amphibious ability, but takes a &ndash;2 penalty to Fortitude saving throws</p>\n<p>11 <strong>Hypertrichosis </strong>Target gains a +1 bonus to its AC, but the max Dex bonus of armor it wears decreases by 1</p>\n<p>12&ndash;13 <strong>Musk gland </strong>Target gains a 30-foot aura that nauseates living creatures within it (Fortitude DC = 10 + half the target&rsquo;s level or CR + the target&rsquo;s Con modifier)</p>\n<p>14&ndash;15 <strong>Secondary Ears </strong>Target gains vulnerability to sonic damage and a +4 bonus to hearing-based Perception checks</p>\n<p>16&ndash;17 <strong>Vestigial limb </strong>Target grows a useless extra limb that imparts a &ndash;2 penalty to Dexterity-based skill checks</p>\n<p>18&ndash;19 <strong>Weeping Sores </strong>Target takes a &ndash;2 penalty to Charisma-based skill checks 20 Wracking Pain Target is sickened</p>","img":"worlds/sandbox_impulsedrive/adv/S01E14/images/NPC-Hesper.jpg"}
